er's","type":"gear","data":{"description":"<div class=\"swade-core savage-eberron-core\">\n<p>This set of clothes consists of boots, a wool skirt or breeches, a sturdy belt, a shirt (perhaps with a vest or jacket), and an ample cloak with a hood.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":2,"equippable":false,"equipped":false,"isVehicular":false,"mods":1},"sort":900000,"flags":{"journal-links":{},"core":{"sourceId":"Item.RyeCbfEjKOWwkLXn"}},"img":"modules/game-icons-net/blackbackground/shirt.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"permission":{"default":0}},{"_id":"E0UfZaXW7ceeb7mZ","name":"Backpack","type":"gear","data":{"description":"<div class=\"swade-core savage-eberron-core\">\n<p>This leather knapsack has one large pocket that closes with a buckled strap and holds about 2 cubic feet of material. Some may have one or more smaller pockets on the sides.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"quantity":1,"weight":2,"price":2,"equippable":false,"equipped":false,"isVehicular":false,"mods":1},"sort":5100000,"flags":{"journal-links":{},"core":{"sourceId":"Item.EJwgrkGHCSHskUnO"}},"img":"modules/game-icons-net/blackbackground/backpack.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"permission":{"default":0}},{"_id":"8w2SYbIrLQhIb2hw","name":"Bedroll","type":"gear","data":{"description":"<div class=\"swade-core savage-eberron-core\">\n<p>This consists of two woolen sheets sewn together along the bottom and one side to create a bag for sleeping in. Some have cloth straps along the open side so the bedroll can be tied closed while you are sleeping. It can be rolled and tied into a tight coil for storage or transport. Most people use a blanket with the bedroll to stay warm or provide a ground cushion.</p>\n</div>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"quantity":1,"weight":3,"price":1,"equippable":false,"equipped":false,"isVehicular":false,"mods":1},"sort":5300000,"flags":{"journal-links":{},"core":{"sourceId":"Item.u4QC3ltQoRK2ucM7"}},"img":"modules/game-ico